# Phase 1: Foundation

## What to Build
Set up the Laravel project with the complete database schema, multi-tenant middleware, authentication for both admin and patient portal, and role-based access control.

## Reference
Read SPEC.md sections 2 (Architecture), 3 (Database Schema), and 5 (Roles).

## Tasks

